					<REFEX CASE="plain" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="nominal" TYPE="name">Pumori</REFEX>
				</ORIGINAL-REFEX>
			</REFERENCE>
			<STRING> (or Pumo Ri) is a mountain in the Himalaya on the Nepal-Tibet border.</STRING>
