					<REFEX CASE="plain" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="nominal" TYPE="name">Pumori</REFEX>
				</ORIGINAL-REFEX>
			</REFERENCE>
			<STRING> is a popular climbing peak and the easiest route is graded class 3, although with avalanche danger.</STRING>
