				</ORIGINAL-REFEX>
			</REFERENCE>
			<STRING> was first climbed in 1962 by Gerhard Lenser of a German-Swiss expedition.Two Czechs (Leopold Sulovsky and Michalec Zeduak) climbed a new route on the South face in the spring of 1996 (Joe Simpson, 1997, Dark Shadows falling). </STRING>
		</SENTENCE>
